widget.name: Open Incidents Pending Attribution
widget.query: -category:job and expanseassetorganizationunit:"" and type:"Expanse Issue" and -status:Closed

widget.name: Open Incidents With High / Critical Severity
widget.query: -category:job and -status:archived and -status:closed and type:"Expanse Issue" and severity:>=High

widget.name: Open Incidents
widget.query: type:"Expanse Issue" and (severity:High or severity:Critical or severity:Medium) -status:Closed

widget.name: Open Incidents on GCP By Region
widget.query: -status:archived and -status:closed and type:"Expanse Issue" and expanseprovider:"Google"

widget.name: Open Incidents on Azure By Region
widget.query: -status:archived and -status:closed and type:"Expanse Issue" and expanseprovider:"Microsoft Azure"

widget.name: Open Incidents on AWS By Region
widget.query: -status:archived and -status:closed and type:"Expanse Issue" and expanseprovider:"Amazon web services"
